,"name":"Cap Batch Volume"},{"parameters":{"keys":{"key":[{"currentKey":"id","newKey":"leadId"}]},"additionalOptions":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.renameKeys","typeVersion":1,"position":[3294,400],"id":"332a4059-9184-4494-b24a-fc44d39e0fe0","name":"Align Field Names"},{"parameters":{"content":"### New Lead Form Submission\n\nServes an n8n-hosted form (Email, Company, Score). Each submission becomes one execution.\n\nNext: Route by Work Type","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"1e4afc66-4264-97df-abd0-f895ff35067b","name":"Note: New Lead Form Submission"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Route by Work Type\n\nRoutes each item to one of 4 lanes: standard, priority, vip + fallback.\n\nPorts: ①→ Process 'standard' → Airtable · ②→ Fast-Track 'priority' + Alert · ③→ Fast-Track 'vip' + Alert · ④→ Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"9a886f36-469b-8ef9-acd3-e504df83f6c3","name":"Note: Route by Work Type"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Process 'standard' → Airtable\n\nairtable — `upsert` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Merge Routed Work\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,250],"id":"8b9c6794-12e1-1232-963a-0cd62a597584","name":"Note: Process 'standard' → Airtable"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fast-Track 'priority' + Alert\n\ngmail — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Merge Routed Work\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,760],"id":"b4501e31-1b1a-ce30-bc52-f5bc869e72a7","name":"Note: Fast-Track 'priority' + Alert"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fast-Track 'vip' + Alert\n\ngmail — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Merge Routed Work\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,1270],"id":"2b3c0ca1-fd67-2cb0-a63b-323850aee502","name":"Note: Fast-Track 'vip' + Alert"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)\n\nairtable — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Merge Routed Work\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,1780],"id":"99d0fb36-3e7a-f24d-ef8c-e9532ec1fdb3","name":"Note: Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Merge Routed Work\n\nRejoins 4 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Cap Batch Volume","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,520],"id":"1330485c-05be-c522-dbe4-a5c719afaa2f","name":"Note: Merge Routed Work"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Cap Batch Volume\n\nCaps the stream at 100 items to protect downstream quotas.\n\nNext: Align Field Names","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,520],"id":"ea99690e-8781-9c2d-b06a-73b2312a192e","name":"Note: Cap Batch Volume"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Align Field Names\n\nNormalizes field names so every source feeds the same downstream schema.","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,520],"id":"15e22440-7b35-62a6-8e22-223c1eb614bc","name":"Note: Align Field Names"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Save form submissions with Airtable and Gmail\n\n**Pattern:** Form Intake · **Level:** Foundation · **Trigger:** Form\n\n## What it does\nSave form submissions with Airtable and Gmail. It starts from a hosted form submission.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual enrichment is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nNew Lead Form Submission → Route by Work Type → Process 'standard' → Airtable → Merge Routed Work → Cap Batch Volume → Align Field Names\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to form intake without manual effort\n- Anyone automating enrichment in sales\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Saves hours of manual work each week\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n- Removes copy-paste errors\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Airtable PAT; Google OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"0bb6ad4d-dcb0-145c-c8a9-12ef51b20942","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your enrichment process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-290],"id":"db4320cf-002f-fc8a-3209-f90367de5835","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"New Lead Form Submission":{"main":[[{"node":"Route by Work Type","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Route by Work Type":{"main":[[{"node":"Process 'standard' → Airtable","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Fast-Track 'priority' + Alert","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Fast-Track 'vip' + Alert","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Process 'standard' → Airtable":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Routed Work","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fast-Track 'priority' + Alert":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Routed Work","type":"main","index":1}]]},"Fast-Track 'vip' + Alert":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Routed Work","type":"main","index":2}]]},"Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Routed Work","type":"main","index":3}]]},"Merge Routed Work":{"main":[[{"node":"Cap Batch Volume","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Cap Batch Volume":{"main":[[{"node":"Align Field Names","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"1ffeedfc-eab1-4155-9282-ecca8fe78fd3","id":"FDX04724"}